    "Though proposals on multimodal fusion for on-device inference do exist [19], [21], [24], t-READi is still the first to design such a system for autonomous driving with practical considerations, i.e., robustness and efficiency in driving environments.",
    "The rest of the paper is organized as follows.§ II introduces the background and motivation.",
    "The detailed system design and implementation are described in § III and § IV, respectively.",
    "§ V reports the evaluation results.",
    "Related works are presented in § VI, along with limitations and future directions of t-READi."
  ],
